        <num>50-3-2</num>
        <content>
          <p>The following is adopted as the pledge of allegiance to the state flag:</p>
          <p>"I pledge allegiance to the Georgia flag and to the principles for which it stands: Wisdom, Justice, and Moderation."</p>
